name: New Holland 9682 4WD Tractor FS22
description:
Based off of the in game Versatile. You can choose from single, dual, and triple tires. Front Weights, as well as PTO and 3 Point Linkage options. Other features is an opening door, realistic dashboard, and UDIM Glass for a more realistic appearance. More model number options to come later.

Consider supporting my work on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/whiskeysierramodding
